{
  "id": "adv_main_03_09_01",
  "title": "BIG4編1章41話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "一人ひとりが起こした嵐を掛け合わせる。そして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll combine the storms that each of us creates. And…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4643.8777142,
          "startTime": 5.4438777142
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "私達四人で、一つの……大きな嵐を作ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll create a single… big storm with the four of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4438777142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 12.2611121019
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 12.5111121019
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、最近ぐっと調子が良くなってきたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ you’ve all really been getting into your groove lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.3111121019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "私達の……四人だからこそ出せる強みを\n見つけられたおかげだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it’s because we were able to find\nthe strengths that we can only show as a group of four.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7333345413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ぼんやりとしていた手応えがはっきりしたので\n改善もしやすくなりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that we have a clear grasp of what we were vaguely feeling before‚\nit’s become easier to make improvements.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9333345413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルもどんどん楽しくなってきたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live battles are getting more and more fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2554206848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "楽しいだけでなく連戦連勝……まさに絶好調ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not only are they fun‚ but we’re on a winning streak… We’re in top form!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1421436628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺から見てもみんなの成長が分かるよ\n……この様子なら大丈夫だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even I can see how much you’ve all grown.\n…At this rate‚ I think we’ll be fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2727159341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、今度生放送の音楽番組があるんだが\n月ストで出演してみないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey everyone‚ there’s a live music program coming up‚\nand I was wondering if Moon Tempest would like to appear on it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7393826008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 55.4999951045
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "生放送……ですか\nそういえば、四人でのお仕事は初めてですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A live broadcast…?\nNow that you mention it‚ this is the first time we’ve done a job as a group of four.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4999951045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "時期はいつ頃なんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When will it be?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.8337760607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんとの再戦より前なんだ\n実はこの話はかなり前からいただいていてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’ll be before the rematch with DoriKyun.\nActually‚ I received this offer a while ago‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1999951045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃がいた時に話すつもりだったんだが……\n話すに話せなくなっていたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and I was planning to tell you all when Kotono was still here…\nbut I never got the chance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5931151638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃がいた時にいただいたオファーとなると……\nもう流れてしまっているのではなくて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it’s an offer you received when Kotono was still here…\nisn’t it gone already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.0085445005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それが、先方は「四人でもぜひ！」とおっしゃって\nいてな。返事もぎりぎりまで待っていただいているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ they said they would “definitely love to have you even with four members‚”\nand they’ve been waiting until the last minute for our reply.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.182874348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……だから私達が落ち着いたタイミングで\n話してくれたという訳ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… So you waited to tell us\nuntil we were in a better place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.26611708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことだ。とはいえ、今はどりきゅんとの\n再戦に集中したいということであれば――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. But if you’d rather focus\non the rematch with DoriKyun right now--",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2994504134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "出ます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9483847775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 103.6179064112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "お、おぉ……そんなに即答でいいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ oh… You’re sure about that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.6179064112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと前までの私達なら、自信がないし\n周りの目も気にしちゃってましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A little while ago‚ we would’ve been unsure and\nworried about what others thought…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7999951045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "今の私達に怖いものはありませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re not afraid of anything now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.7612847802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "どんとこーい！　って感じ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bring it on!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2601507344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、私達全員……やる気満々です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ we’re all… totally pumped!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3218174216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。先方に伝えておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright. I’ll let them know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9884838499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――音楽番組生放送当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the live music program",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.6815660712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.5815660712
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.5815660712
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_live-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 132.7482266344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "MC",
      "speakerNameEn": "MC",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さあ、続いてのゲストは～……ただいまいろんな意味で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And now for our next guests~… The group that’s causing a stir for all sorts of reasons!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5482266344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "MC",
      "speakerNameEn": "MC",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "話題沸騰中！　月のテンペスト～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.7333284378,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3766.66666669999,
          "startTime": 141.4999951045
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "よろしくお願いしま～す！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pleased to be here~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.1453461882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.0375778114
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.7974858641
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（この番組はパフォーマンス前にかなり突っ込んだ）\n（話をすることで有名だ。何事もなければいいが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This program is famous for asking pretty tough questions）\n（before the performance. Hopefully‚ nothing bad happens…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.7974858641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
